      "text": [
        " عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: «يُسْتَحَبُّ لِلْمَرِيضِ أَنْ يُعْطِيَ اَلسَّائِلَ بِيَدِهِ وَ يَأْمُرَ اَلسَّائِلَ أَنْ يَدْعُوَ لَهُ»."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1732 - Imam (as) said:\n\"It is recommended for a sick person to give to the beggar with his own hand and to ask the beggar to pray for him.\""
        ]
      }
